ZH: 我爷爷有一座马厩。
EN: My grandfather has a stable.

ZH: 这个农场有一个大马厩。
EN: This farm has a big stable.

ZH: 她经营着一个马厩来养马。
EN: She runs a stable to breed horses.

ZH: 马厩里的马正在休息。
EN: The horses in the stable are resting.

ZH: 这个马厩有很好的空调系统。
EN: This stable has a very good air conditioning system.

ZH: 他正在马厩里擦洗马匹。
EN: He is grooming the horses in the stable.

ZH: 马厩的地面铺着稻草。
EN: The stable's floor is covered with straw.

ZH: 昨晚一场大火烧毁了马厩。
EN: A big fire destroyed the stable last night.

ZH: 马厩的门口贴着“慎入”标志。
EN: There is a "Caution" sign at the entrance of the stable.

ZH: 这座马厩可以容纳二十匹马。
EN: This stable can accommodate twenty horses.

ZH: 在马厩里，你可以学习如何骑马。
EN: In the stable, you can learn how to ride a horse.

ZH: 马厩里充满了马的气味。
EN: The stable is filled with the smell of horses.

ZH: 马厩的墙壁被涂成了红色。
EN: The walls of the stable are painted red.

ZH: 你可以在马厩里喂马。
EN: You can feed the horses in the stable.

ZH: 马厩的顶部有一个天窗。
EN: There is a skylight on top of the stable.

ZH: 我花了一个下午打扫了马厩。
EN: I spent an afternoon cleaning the stable.

ZH: 小张每天早上都会去马厩锻炼。
EN: Xiao Zhang goes to the stable for exercise every morning.

ZH: 马厩的门是木质的。
EN: The stable's door is made of wood.

ZH: 我的梦想是拥有一个自己的马厩。
EN: My dream is to have my own stable.

ZH: 马厩的旁边有一个草地供马儿奔跑。
EN: There is a pasture next to the stable for the horses to run.
